descr: around 21h i decided to fill in all the hours for the rest of the day on the sheet since I knew what activities i would be doing and how much light i would be exposed to. looking back; I think the estimates were correct

descr: on the streets, many people looked at me, or at least more than normal. at work, some people asked if I was filming them, and in general many people were curious especially about the glasses. i shared the story at least 10 times today, most thought it was interesting but would not want to participate or could not due to a prescription of glasses
future_use: well I will probably have to tell the story at least 20 more times I expect, so maybe it would be handy to keep to link to the webpage ready
